  id: 35
  title: "Nh\u1EADt k\xFD h\xE0ng x\xF3m #18 \u2014 \xD4ng gi\xE0 \u1EDF t\u1EA7ng
    15"
  category: 3
  content: "78 tu\u1ED5i, s\u1ED1ng m\u1ED9t m\xECnh. V\u1EE3 m\u1EA5t n\u0103m ngo\xE1i.
    Con c\xE1i \u1EDF n\u01B0\u1EDBc ngo\xE0i, g\u1ECDi \u0111i\u1EC7n kh\xF4ng \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c
    \u2014 m\u1EA1ng b\u1ECB c\u1EAFt. T\xF4i vi\u1EBFt d\xF2ng n\xE0y \u1EDF ban
    c\xF4ng t\u1EA7ng 15, nh\xECn xu\u1ED1ng \u0111\u01B0\u1EDDng. Qu\xE2n \u0111\u1ED9i
    \u0111\xE3 b\u1ECF \u0111i. Xe b\u1ECDc th\xE9p c\xF2n \u0111\u1ED7 d\u01B0\u1EDBi
    \u0111\xF3 nh\u01B0ng kh\xF4ng ai trong. T\xF4i th\u1EA5y c\xF3 thanh ni\xEAn
    \u0111ang ch\u1EA1y v\u1EC1 ph\xEDa c\u1EA7u. C\u1EA7u \u0111\xE3 g\xE3y t\u1EEB
    h\xF4m qua \u2014 anh ta kh\xF4ng bi\u1EBFt. T\xF4i h\xE9t nh\u01B0ng ti\u1EBFng
    t\xF4i kh\xF4ng \u0111\u1EE7 l\u1EDBn. Ch\xFAc may m\u1EAFn, con trai."
  image: {fileID: 0}
  voiceLog: {fileID: 0}
